1) program to convert string into following format
--------------------------------------------------------------------
s=input('enter string')
n=len(s)
c=1 
k=0
res=''
for i in range(1,n):
    if s[i]==s[k]:
        c=c+1 
    else:
        res=res+str(c)+s[k]
        k=i 
        c=1 
    if i==n-1:
        res=res+str(c)+s[k]
print(res)
---------------------------------------------------------
Output:
enter stringaabbeddd
2a2b1e3d
